This is a comprehensive dealership management system with features including:
- Vehicle inventory management
- Appraisals
- Sales tracking
- Customer reviews
- Forms management
- Multi-tenant support (dealers)
- Calendar/scheduling
- Aftercare cases

The codebase uses:
- Next.js (pages router)
- MongoDB with Mongoose models
- NextAuth for authentication
- Multi-tenant architecture with Dealer model
